            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                What are your delivery areas?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion1">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                We currently deliver to all areas within Jakarta. For locations outside Jakarta, please contact us to arrange special delivery options. Delivery fees vary based on distance.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
